over what I had been doing.

35:36.125 --> 35:39.625
- Did you break it off?
- I did, but it was too late.

35:39.625 --> 35:43.250
The university found out that
Red was sleeping with a student

35:43.250 --> 35:48.083
and Bill Marsh covered it up,
but he forced Red to resign

35:48.083 --> 35:50.750
and Emily left him.

35:54.291 --> 35:57.000
- I ruined Red's life.
- Oh, hold on, Vanessa.

35:57.000 --> 35:59.834
Red knew exactly
what he was doing. Okay?

35:59.834 --> 36:01.792
Now he was in a position
of responsibility

36:01.792 --> 36:03.875
and you were nothing more
than a student.

36:03.875 --> 36:05.625
Well, he was 25.

36:05.625 --> 36:09.000
He was six years older than me.
We were kids.

36:09.000 --> 36:12.166
Stupid, reckless kids.

36:12.166 --> 36:15.834
And we hurt a woman
who didn't deserve it.

36:20.000 --> 36:22.667
So now you know.

36:22.667 --> 36:24.166
I do.

36:26.000 --> 36:29.458
Do you really think we made
a mistake moving in together?

36:29.458 --> 36:32.083
Oh.

36:32.083 --> 36:34.375
Not even close.

36:45.291 --> 36:48.458
Good morning, darlin'.
What's wrong, sugar?

36:48.458 --> 36:51.542
This special assignment
my law professor gave me.

36:51.542 --> 36:52.875
