37:21.291 --> 37:22.875
Yes.

37:22.875 --> 37:25.458
We're in Parrish's
law seminar together.

37:26.708 --> 37:28.166
'Oh, wow.
What's the big secret?'

37:28.166 --> 37:29.708
Nothing.

37:29.708 --> 37:32.041
