38:13.750 --> 38:16.458
- It's Kobayashi Maru.
- Huh?

38:16.458 --> 38:17.792
Kobayashi Maru
from "Star Trek."

38:17.792 --> 38:20.500
- The TV show?
- Ah, yes.

38:20.500 --> 38:22.792
And successful film franchise.

38:22.792 --> 38:24.834
Eighty five million
opening weekend?

38:24.834 --> 38:26.792
