The Kobayashi Maru scenario
is a test

38:28.959 --> 38:31.125
that Starfleet Academy
gives its cadets.

38:31.125 --> 38:34.750
It's an impossible task to see
how you deal with failure.

38:34.750 --> 38:36.375
Why?

